50\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br><strong>Analyze<\\/strong> my existing Java agent code to see exactly how many API calls are made to lotus.domino.* API to help me estimate good candidates for conversion to Groovy \\/ Grails.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/05-grails-framework.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/05-grails-framework.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Use the powerful Grails framework and Groovy programming language to <strong>interact<\\/strong> with my data in a more natural, object-oriented way (in addition to using SQL).\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br><strong>Eliminate<\\/strong> unnecessary views from my Notes databases because they clutter my design and slow down performance for large databases.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/07-performance.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/07-performance.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br><strong>Performance<\\/strong> optimize the necessary sections of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/08-slowest-url.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/08-slowest-url.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Gain insight into the slowest URLs of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications so I can improve my customer\\u2019s web experience.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Keep my Notes data in the NSF while <em>also<\\/em> having it available using true SQL served by a true RDBMS. (currently unidirectional)\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Avoid <strong>costly<\\/strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/11-use-true-sql-language.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/11-use-true-sql-language.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Use<strong> true SQL<\\/strong> language queries to report on my data \\u2014 even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/12-security-model.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/12-security-model.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Mix the mature security model, reliable replication technology for clustered \\/ off-line use, and rapid application NoSQL-style development of Notes with cutting-edge dynamic language technology from coders <em>so<\\/em> good at Java they invented something even better: Groovy\\/Grails.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br><strong>Avoid<\\/strong> learning SQL by using modern language syntax to write natural coder-friendly statements like: <em>&lt;em&gt;book = Book.findByTitleLike(\\\"Harry Pot%\\u201d)\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/14-professional-database-tools.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/14-professional-database-tools.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Use professional RDBMS database tools such as Navicat\\u00ae Data Modeler Essentials\\u00ae\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br><strong>Stop worrying<\\/strong> that my Notes views have too many documents in them by optionally eliminating the reporting views and shifting that workload to more appropriate SQL queries and reports.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/16-crystal-report.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/16-crystal-report.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Use the industry-leading Crystal Reports\\u00ae natively against my data to produce nice graphs.\",\"\"]]', 'bullets and pics', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '119-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-28 19:42:51', '2014-10-28 19:42:51', '', '119', 'http://dev.grails4notes.com/?p=163', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
