t=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br><strong>Analyze<\\/strong> my existing Java agent code to see exactly how many API calls are made to lotus.domino.* API to help me estimate good candidates for conversion to Groovy \\/ Grails.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/05-grails-framework.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/05-grails-framework.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Use the powerful Grails framework and Groovy programming language to <strong>interact<\\/strong> with my data in a more natural, object-oriented way (in addition to using SQL).\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br><strong>Eliminate<\\/strong> unnecessary views from my Notes databases because they clutter my design and slow down performance for large databases.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/07-performance.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/07-performance.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br><strong>Performance<\\/strong> optimize the necessary sections of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/08-slowest-url.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/08-slowest-url.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Gain insight into the slowest URLs of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications so I can improve my customer\\u2019s web experience.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Keep my Notes data in the NSF while <em>also<\\/em> having it available using true SQL served by a true RDBMS. (currently unidirectional)\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Avoid <strong>costly<\\/strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/11-use-true-sql-language.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/11-use-true-sql-language.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Use<strong> true SQL<\\/strong> language queries to report on my data \\u2014 even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\",\"\"],[\"<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/12-security-model.png\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/199.103.7.19\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/12-security-model.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" class=\\\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\"<br><br>Mix the