n any available virtualization technology. CrossOver does not require an underlying Windows license and provides less CPU overhead therefore a much longer battery life.</p>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://domino4wine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/crossOverLogo.png\" alt=\"domino_Designer\" width=\"437\" height=\"437\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-413\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; color: #6B0031; padding-top: 10px;\">Help get more support for fixing the remaining few non-critical bugs -- spread the word!</h3>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#fff\" padding=\"0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; color: #6B0031; padding-top: 10px;\">Setup Guide</h3>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_half]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right; top: 50%; color: #6B0031; padding-top: 160px;\">Lotus Notes on Linux and Mac OS X </h3>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://domino4wine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/domino_Notes.png\" alt=\"domino_Notes\" width=\"610\" height=\"437\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-415\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#fff\" padding=\"0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_half]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right; top: 50%; color: #6B0031; padding-top: 160px;\">Lotus Notes on Linux and Mac OS X </h3>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://domino4wine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/domino_Administrator.png\" alt=\"domino_Administrator\" width=\"610\" height=\"437\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-412\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_half]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right; top: 50%; color: #6B0031; padding-top: 160px;\">Lotus Notes on Linux and 