t=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_fourth]\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Avoid <strong>costly</strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.</p>\n[button link=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_half last]\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\n[/one_half]\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\n[raw]\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\n[raw]\n[one_fourth]\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11-use-true-sql-language.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_fourth]\nUse<strong> true SQL</strong> language queries to report on my data — even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_half last]\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\n[/one_half]\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\n[raw]\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\n[raw]\n[one_fourth]\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12-security-model.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_fourth]\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Mix the mature security model, reliable replication technology for clustered / off-line use, and rapid application NoSQL-style development of Notes with cutting-edge dynamic language technology from coders <em>so</em> good at Java they invented something even better: Groovy/Grails.</p>\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_half last]\n[/one_half]\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\n[raw]\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\n[raw]\n[one_fourth]\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_fourth]\n<strong>Avoid</strong> learning SQL by using modern language syntax to write natural coder-friendly statements like: </br> <em>book = Book.findByTitleLike(\"Harry Pot%”)</em>\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_half last]\n[/one_half]\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\n[raw]\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\n[raw]\n[one_fourth]\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/14-professional-database-tools.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_fourth]\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use professional RDBMS database tools such as Navicat® Data Modeler Essentials®</p>\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_half last]\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\n[/one_half]\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\n[raw]\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\n[raw]\n[one_fourth]\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_fourth]\n<strong>Stop worrying</strong> that my Notes views have too many documents in them by optionally eliminating the reporting views and shifting that workload to more appropriate SQL queries and reports.\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_half last]\n[/one_half]\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\n[raw]\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\n[raw]\n[one_fourth]\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/16-crystal-report.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_fourth]\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use the industry-leading Crystal Reports® natively against my data to produce nice graphs.</p>\n[button link=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\n[/one_fourth]\n[one_half last]\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\n[/one_half]\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]\n\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\n[raw]\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\n[clear]\n[/raw]\n[/section]', 'I wish I could…', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-17 13:39:49', '2014-11-17 13:39:49', '', '14', 'http://dev.grails4notes.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('332', '2', '2014-11-17 12:46:43', '2014-11-17 12:46:43', '<style>\r\n.g4nraiButton {\r\n-moz-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\n-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbox-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbackground-color:#abbf77;\r\n-moz-border-radius:4px;\r\n-webkit-border-radius:4px;\r\nborder-radius:4px;\r\nborder:1px solid #4b8f29;\r\ndisplay:inline-block;\r\ncursor:pointer;\r\ncolor:#ffffff;\r\nfont-family:arial;\r\nfont-size:26px !important;\r\nfont-weight:bold;\r\npadding:20px 76px !important;\r\ntext-decoration:none;\r\ntext-shadow:1px 2px 11px #5b8a3c;\r\nmargin:auto;\r\ntext-align:center;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:hover {\r\nbackground-color:#e0f2b6;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:active {\r\nposition:relative;\r\ntop:1px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-126\" style=\"vertical align: middle; margin: auto;\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/01-stop-writing-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p><strong>Stop</strong> writing custom Java or Lotuscript agents to query Notes data in a more complex fashion than can be done with view selection formula syntax.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/1.1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"12px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_third][/one_third]\r\n[one_third]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[/one_third]\r\n[one_third last][/one_third]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/02-business-object-model-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Develop</strong> a true <em>Business Object Model</em> for the data in my Notes databases.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/03-formal-documentation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[box style=\"1\"]\r\nEasily create formal documentation in the industry-standard JavaDoc-like format for all of my fields and shared fields on all of my forms and subforms in Notes.\r\n[/box]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/04-analyze-existing-java-agent.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Analyze</strong> my existing Java agent code to see exactly how many API calls are made to lotus.domino.* API to help me estimate good candidates for conversion to Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignrleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/4.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/05-grails-framework.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p>Use the powerful Grails framework and Groovy programming language to <strong>interact</strong> with my data in a more natural, object-oriented way (in addition to using SQL).</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/5.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Eliminate</strong> unnecessary views from my Notes databases because they clutter my design and slow down performance for large databases.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/s6.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/07-performance.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Performance</strong> optimize the necessary sections of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/7.1.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/08-slowest-url.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Gain insight into the slowest URLs of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications so I can improve my customer’s web experience.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/8.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nKeep my Notes data in the NSF while <em>also</em> having it available using true SQL served by a true RDBMS. (currently unidirectional)\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/9.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Avoid <strong>costly</strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11-use-true-sql-language.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nUse<strong> true SQL</strong> language queries to report on my data — even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12-security-model.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Mix the mature security model, reliable replication technology for clustered / off-line use, and rapid application NoSQL-style development of Notes with cutting-edge dynamic language technology from coders <em>so</em> good at Java they invented something even better: Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Avoid</strong> learning SQL by using modern language syntax to write natural coder-friendly statements like: </br> <em>book = Book.findByTitleLike(\"Harry Pot%”)</em>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/14-professional-database-tools.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use professional RDBMS database tools such as Navicat® Data Modeler Essentials®</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Stop worrying</strong> that my Notes views have too many documents in them by optionally eliminating the reporting views and shifting that workload to more appropriate SQL queries and reports.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/16-crystal-report.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use the industry-leading Crystal Reports® natively against my data to produce nice graphs.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]', 'I wish I could…', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-17 12:46:43', '2014-11-17 12:46:43', '', '14', 'http://dev.grails4notes.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('335', '2', '2014-11-17 13:35:25', '2014-11-17 13:35:25', '<style>\r\n.g4nraiButton {\r\n-moz-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\n-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbox-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbackground-color: #abbf77;\r\n-moz-border-radius: 4px;\r\n-webkit-border-radius: 4px;\r\nborder-radius: 4px;\r\nborder: 1px solid #4b8f29;\r\ndisplay: block;\r\ncursor: pointer;\r\ncolor: #ffffff;\r\nfont-family: arial;\r\nfont-size: 26px !important;\r\nfont-weight: bold;\r\npadding: 20px 76px !important;\r\ntext-decoration: none;\r\ntext-shadow: 1px 2px 9px #5b8a3c;\r\nmargin:auto;\r\ntext-align:center;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:hover {\r\nbackground-color:#e0f2b6;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:active {\r\nposition:relative;\r\ntop:1px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-126\" style=\"vertical align: middle; margin: auto;\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/01-stop-writing-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p><strong>Stop</strong> writing custom Java or Lotuscript agents to query Notes data in a more complex fashion than can be done with view selection formula syntax.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/1.1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"16px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_third][/one_third]\r\n[one_third]\r\n<a class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</a>\r\n[/one_third]\r\n[one_third last][/one_third]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/02-business-object-model-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Develop</strong> a true <em>Business Object Model</em> for the data in my Notes databases.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/03-formal-documentation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[box style=\"1\"]\r\nEasily create formal documentation in the industry-standard JavaDoc-like format for all of my fields and shared fields on all of my forms and subforms in Notes.\r\n[/box]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/04-analyze-existing-java-agent.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Analyze</strong> my existing Java agent code to see exactly how many API calls are made to lotus.domino.* API to help me estimate good candidates for conversion to Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignrleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/4.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/05-grails-framework.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p>Use the powerful Grails framework and Groovy programming language to <strong>interact</strong> with my data in a more natural, object-oriented way (in addition to using SQL).</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/5.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Eliminate</strong> unnecessary views from my Notes databases because they clutter my design and slow down performance for large databases.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/s6.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/07-performance.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Performance</strong> optimize the necessary sections of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/7.1.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/08-slowest-url.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Gain insight into the slowest URLs of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications so I can improve my customer’s web experience.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/8.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nKeep my Notes data in the NSF while <em>also</em> having it available using true SQL served by a true RDBMS. (currently unidirectional)\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/9.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Avoid <strong>costly</strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11-use-true-sql-language.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nUse<strong> true SQL</strong> language queries to report on my data — even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12-security-model.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Mix the mature security model, reliable replication technology for clustered / off-line use, and rapid application NoSQL-style development of Notes with cutting-edge dynamic language technology from coders <em>so</em> good at Java they invented something even better: Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Avoid</strong> learning SQL by using modern language syntax to write natural coder-friendly statements like: </br> <em>book = Book.findByTitleLike(\"Harry Pot%”)</em>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/14-professional-database-tools.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use professional RDBMS database tools such as Navicat® Data Modeler Essentials®</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Stop worrying</strong> that my Notes views have too many documents in them by optionally eliminating the reporting views and shifting that workload to more appropriate SQL queries and reports.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/16-crystal-report.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use the industry-leading Crystal Reports® natively against my data to produce nice graphs.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]', 'I wish I could…', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-17 13:35:25', '2014-11-17 13:35:25', '', '14', 'http://dev.grails4notes.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('333', '2', '2014-11-17 12:52:49', '2014-11-17 12:52:49', '<style>\r\n.g4nraiButton {\r\n-moz-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\n-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbox-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbackground-color: #abbf77;\r\n-moz-border-radius: 4px;\r\n-webkit-border-radius: 4px;\r\nborder-radius: 4px;\r\nborder: 1px solid #4b8f29;\r\ndisplay: block;\r\ncursor: pointer;\r\ncolor: #ffffff;\r\nfont-family: arial;\r\nfont-size: 26px !important;\r\nfont-weight: bold;\r\npadding: 20px 76px !important;\r\ntext-decoration: none;\r\ntext-shadow: 1px 2px 9px #5b8a3c;\r\nmargin:auto;\r\ntext-align:center;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:hover {\r\nbackground-color:#e0f2b6;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:active {\r\nposition:relative;\r\ntop:1px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-126\" style=\"vertical align: middle; margin: auto;\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/01-stop-writing-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p><strong>Stop</strong> writing custom Java or Lotuscript agents to query Notes data in a more complex fashion than can be done with view selection formula syntax.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/1.1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"12px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_third][/one_third]\r\n[one_third]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[/one_third]\r\n[one_third last][/one_third]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/02-business-object-model-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Develop</strong> a true <em>Business Object Model</em> for the data in my Notes databases.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/03-formal-documentation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[box style=\"1\"]\r\nEasily create formal documentation in the industry-standard JavaDoc-like format for all of my fields and shared fields on all of my forms and subforms in Notes.\r\n[/box]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/04-analyze-existing-java-agent.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Analyze</strong> my existing Java agent code to see exactly how many API calls are made to lotus.domino.* API to help me estimate good candidates for conversion to Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignrleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/4.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/05-grails-framework.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p>Use the powerful Grails framework and Groovy programming language to <strong>interact</strong> with my data in a more natural, object-oriented way (in addition to using SQL).</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/5.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Eliminate</strong> unnecessary views from my Notes databases because they clutter my design and slow down performance for large databases.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/s6.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/07-performance.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Performance</strong> optimize the necessary sections of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/7.1.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/08-slowest-url.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Gain insight into the slowest URLs of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications so I can improve my customer’s web experience.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/8.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nKeep my Notes data in the NSF while <em>also</em> having it available using true SQL served by a true RDBMS. (currently unidirectional)\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/9.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Avoid <strong>costly</strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11-use-true-sql-language.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nUse<strong> true SQL</strong> language queries to report on my data — even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12-security-model.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Mix the mature security model, reliable replication technology for clustered / off-line use, and rapid application NoSQL-style development of Notes with cutting-edge dynamic language technology from coders <em>so</em> good at Java they invented something even better: Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Avoid</strong> learning SQL by using modern language syntax to write natural coder-friendly statements like: </br> <em>book = Book.findByTitleLike(\"Harry Pot%”)</em>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/14-professional-database-tools.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use professional RDBMS database tools such as Navicat® Data Modeler Essentials®</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Stop worrying</strong> that my Notes views have too many documents in them by optionally eliminating the reporting views and shifting that workload to more appropriate SQL queries and reports.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/16-crystal-report.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use the industry-leading Crystal Reports® natively against my data to produce nice graphs.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]', 'I wish I could…', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-17 12:52:49', '2014-11-17 12:52:49', '', '14', 'http://dev.grails4notes.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('334', '2', '2014-11-17 12:53:51', '2014-11-17 12:53:51', '<style>\r\n.g4nraiButton {\r\n-moz-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\n-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbox-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbackground-color: #abbf77;\r\n-moz-border-radius: 4px;\r\n-webkit-border-radius: 4px;\r\nborder-radius: 4px;\r\nborder: 1px solid #4b8f29;\r\ndisplay: block;\r\ncursor: pointer;\r\ncolor: #ffffff;\r\nfont-family: arial;\r\nfont-size: 26px !important;\r\nfont-weight: bold;\r\npadding: 20px 76px !important;\r\ntext-decoration: none;\r\ntext-shadow: 1px 2px 9px #5b8a3c;\r\nmargin:auto;\r\ntext-align:center;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:hover {\r\nbackground-color:#e0f2b6;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:active {\r\nposition:relative;\r\ntop:1px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-126\" style=\"vertical align: middle; margin: auto;\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/01-stop-writing-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p><strong>Stop</strong> writing custom Java or Lotuscript agents to query Notes data in a more complex fashion than can be done with view selection formula syntax.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/1.1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"16px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_third][/one_third]\r\n[one_third]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[/one_third]\r\n[one_third last][/one_third]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/02-business-object-model-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Develop</strong> a true <em>Business Object Model</em> for the data in my Notes databases.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/03-formal-documentation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[box style=\"1\"]\r\nEasily create formal documentation in the industry-standard JavaDoc-like format for all of my fields and shared fields on all of my forms and subforms in Notes.\r\n[/box]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/04-analyze-existing-java-agent.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Analyze</strong> my existing Java agent code to see exactly how many API calls are made to lotus.domino.* API to help me estimate good candidates for conversion to Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignrleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/4.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/05-grails-framework.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p>Use the powerful Grails framework and Groovy programming language to <strong>interact</strong> with my data in a more natural, object-oriented way (in addition to using SQL).</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/5.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Eliminate</strong> unnecessary views from my Notes databases because they clutter my design and slow down performance for large databases.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/s6.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/07-performance.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Performance</strong> optimize the necessary sections of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/7.1.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/08-slowest-url.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Gain insight into the slowest URLs of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications so I can improve my customer’s web experience.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/8.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nKeep my Notes data in the NSF while <em>also</em> having it available using true SQL served by a true RDBMS. (currently unidirectional)\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/9.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Avoid <strong>costly</strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11-use-true-sql-language.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nUse<strong> true SQL</strong> language queries to report on my data — even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12-security-model.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Mix the mature security model, reliable replication technology for clustered / off-line use, and rapid application NoSQL-style development of Notes with cutting-edge dynamic language technology from coders <em>so</em> good at Java they invented something even better: Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Avoid</strong> learning SQL by using modern language syntax to write natural coder-friendly statements like: </br> <em>book = Book.findByTitleLike(\"Harry Pot%”)</em>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/14-professional-database-tools.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use professional RDBMS database tools such as Navicat® Data Modeler Essentials®</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Stop worrying</strong> that my Notes views have too many documents in them by optionally eliminating the reporting views and shifting that workload to more appropriate SQL queries and reports.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/16-crystal-report.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use the industry-leading Crystal Reports® natively against my data to produce nice graphs.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]', 'I wish I could…', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-17 12:53:51', '2014-11-17 12:53:51', '', '14', 'http://dev.grails4notes.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('337', '2', '2014-11-17 13:40:33', '2014-11-17 13:40:33', '<style>\r\n.g4nraiButton {\r\n-moz-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\n-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbox-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbackground-color: #abbf77;\r\n-moz-border-radius: 4px;\r\n-webkit-border-radius: 4px;\r\nborder-radius: 4px;\r\nborder: 1px solid #4b8f29;\r\ndisplay: block;\r\ncursor: pointer;\r\ncolor: #ffffff;\r\nfont-family: arial;\r\nfont-size: 26px !important;\r\nfont-weight: bold;\r\npadding: 20px 76px !important;\r\ntext-decoration: none;\r\ntext-shadow: 1px 2px 9px #5b8a3c;\r\nmargin:auto;\r\ntext-align:center;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:hover {\r\nbackground-color:#e0f2b6;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:active {\r\nposition:relative;\r\ntop:1px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-126\" style=\"vertical align: middle; margin: auto;\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/01-stop-writing-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p><strong>Stop</strong> writing custom Java or Lotuscript agents to query Notes data in a more complex fashion than can be done with view selection formula syntax.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/1.1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"16px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_third][/one_third]\r\n[one_third]\r\n<a  href=\"#secondary\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"g4nraiButton\">Request an Invite</button></a>\r\n[/one_third]\r\n[one_third last][/one_third]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/02-business-object-model-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Develop</strong> a true <em>Business Object Model</em> for the data in my Notes databases.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/03-formal-documentation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[box style=\"1\"]\r\nEasily create formal documentation in the industry-standard JavaDoc-like format for all of my fields and shared fields on all of my forms and subforms in Notes.\r\n[/box]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/04-analyze-existing-java-agent.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Analyze</strong> my existing Java agent code to see exactly how many API calls are made to lotus.domino.* API to help me estimate good candidates for conversion to Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignrleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/4.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/05-grails-framework.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p>Use the powerful Grails framework and Groovy programming language to <strong>interact</strong> with my data in a more natural, object-oriented way (in addition to using SQL).</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/5.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Eliminate</strong> unnecessary views from my Notes databases because they clutter my design and slow down performance for large databases.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/s6.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/07-performance.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Performance</strong> optimize the necessary sections of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/7.1.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/08-slowest-url.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Gain insight into the slowest URLs of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications so I can improve my customer’s web experience.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/8.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nKeep my Notes data in the NSF while <em>also</em> having it available using true SQL served by a true RDBMS. (currently unidirectional)\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/9.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Avoid <strong>costly</strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11-use-true-sql-language.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nUse<strong> true SQL</strong> language queries to report on my data — even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12-security-model.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Mix the mature security model, reliable replication technology for clustered / off-line use, and rapid application NoSQL-style development of Notes with cutting-edge dynamic language technology from coders <em>so</em> good at Java they invented something even better: Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Avoid</strong> learning SQL by using modern language syntax to write natural coder-friendly statements like: </br> <em>book = Book.findByTitleLike(\"Harry Pot%”)</em>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/14-professional-database-tools.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use professional RDBMS database tools such as Navicat® Data Modeler Essentials®</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Stop worrying</strong> that my Notes views have too many documents in them by optionally eliminating the reporting views and shifting that workload to more appropriate SQL queries and reports.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/16-crystal-report.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use the industry-leading Crystal Reports® natively against my data to produce nice graphs.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" padding=\"10px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n<button class=\"g4nraiButton\" href=\"#secondary\">Request an Invite</button>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]', 'I wish I could…', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-17 13:40:33', '2014-11-17 13:40:33', '', '14', 'http://dev.grails4notes.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('340', '2', '2014-11-18 07:53:17', '2014-11-18 07:53:17', '<style>\r\n.g4nraiButton {\r\n-moz-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\n-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbox-shadow: 0px 10px 14px -7px #3e7327;\r\nbackground-color: #abbf77;\r\n-moz-border-radius: 4px;\r\n-webkit-border-radius: 4px;\r\nborder-radius: 4px;\r\nborder: 1px solid #4b8f29;\r\ndisplay: block;\r\ncursor: pointer;\r\ncolor: #ffffff;\r\nfont-family: arial;\r\nfont-size: 26px !important;\r\nfont-weight: bold;\r\npadding: 20px 76px !important;\r\ntext-decoration: none;\r\ntext-shadow: 1px 2px 9px #5b8a3c;\r\nmargin:auto;\r\ntext-align:center;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:hover {\r\nbackground-color:#e0f2b6;\r\n}\r\n.g4nraiButton:active {\r\nposition:relative;\r\ntop:1px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-126\" style=\"vertical align: middle; margin: auto;\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/01-stop-writing-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p><strong>Stop</strong> writing custom Java or Lotuscript agents to query Notes data in a more complex fashion than can be done with view selection formula syntax.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]<a href=\"http://www-10.lotus.com/ldd/ddwiki.nsf/dx/Searching_for_Documents\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/1.1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/02-business-object-model-a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Develop</strong> a true <em>Business Object Model</em> for the data in my Notes databases.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/03-formal-documentation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n[box style=\"1\"]\r\nEasily create formal documentation in the industry-standard JavaDoc-like format for all of my fields and shared fields on all of my forms and subforms in Notes.\r\n[/box]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/04-analyze-existing-java-agent.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Analyze</strong> my existing Java agent code to see exactly how many API calls are made to lotus.domino.* API to help me estimate good candidates for conversion to Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img class=\"alignrleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/4.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/05-grails-framework.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p>Use the powerful Grails framework and Groovy programming language to <strong>interact</strong> with my data in a more natural, object-oriented way (in addition to using SQL).</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Domain%20Classes/findBy.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/5.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/06-eliminate-unnecessary-views.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\"><strong>Eliminate</strong> unnecessary views from my Notes databases because they clutter my design and slow down performance for large databases.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.martinscott.com/struturo.nsf/ID/tech_articles_perf_engr\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/s6.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/07-performance.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Performance</strong> optimize the necessary sections of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/7.1.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/08-slowest-url.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Gain insight into the slowest URLs of my Domino classic or newer XPages web applications so I can improve my customer’s web experience.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/8.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/09-keep-my-notes-data.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nKeep my Notes data in the NSF while <em>also</em> having it available using true SQL served by a true RDBMS. (currently unidirectional)\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/9.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10-avoid-costly-sql-licensing.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Avoid <strong>costly</strong> SQL licensing by using the powerful Postgres server which runs on all platforms.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://www.postgresql.org/about/licence/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/10.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11-use-true-sql-language.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\nUse<strong> true SQL</strong> language queries to report on my data — even when it is stored across many NSF databases or servers.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/11.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12-security-model.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Mix the mature security model, reliable replication technology for clustered / off-line use, and rapid application NoSQL-style development of Notes with cutting-edge dynamic language technology from coders <em>so</em> good at Java they invented something even better: Groovy/Grails.</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13-avoid-learning-sql.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Avoid</strong> learning SQL by using modern language syntax to write natural coder-friendly statements like: </br> <em>book = Book.findByTitleLike(\"Harry Pot%”)</em>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/14-professional-database-tools.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use professional RDBMS database tools such as Navicat® Data Modeler Essentials®</p>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#f9f9f9\" padding=\"40px 0\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/15-stop-worrying-that-my-notes.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" />\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<strong>Stop worrying</strong> that my Notes views have too many documents in them by optionally eliminating the reporting views and shifting that workload to more appropriate SQL queries and reports.\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[section bgcolor=\"#2C2C2E\" parallax=\"true\" padding=\"40px 0\" border=\"1px solid #ececec\"]\r\n[raw]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://199.103.7.19/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/16-crystal-report.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" /></a>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<p style=\"color: #FFF\">Use the industry-leading Crystal Reports® natively against my data to produce nice graphs.</p>\r\n[button link=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" color=\"green\" align=\"right\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"small\"]Learn More...[/button]\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n[one_half last]\r\n<a href=\"http://store.businessobjects.com/store/bobjamer/Content/pbPage.sap-crystal-solutions-2013\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://dev.grails4notes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/13.gif\" width=\"627\" height=\"480\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]', 'I wish I could…', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-18 07:53:17', '2014-11-18 07:53:17', '', '14', 'http://dev.grails4notes.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '