 has an NSD hook which is not working and therefore not starting properly.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding: 12px 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.codeweavers.com/store/?dealcode=DOMINO\" class=\"g4nraiButton\"  style=\"width: 100px; color: #fff;\">Buy Now</a></p>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]', 'Domino4Wine', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-23 14:08:39', '2015-01-23 14:08:39', '', '14', 'http://dev.domino4wine.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
