you find on the <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/groups/Domino4Wine-6922320\">LinkedIn group.</a></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"jtLinButton\" style=\"color: #fff; width:300px;\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/groups/Domino4Wine-6922320\">Join the LinkedIn Group!</a></p>\r\n[clear]\r\n[/raw]\r\n[/section]', 'Domino4Wine', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-04 11:54:59', '2015-02-04 11:54:59', '', '14', 'http://dev.domino4wine.com/14-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
